18 Gluttony 5 Makes the Pokémon already eat a held Berry when its HP drops to half or less.
36 Sturdy 3 It cannot be knocked out with one hit. One-hit KO moves cannot knock it out, either.
54 Indigestion 5 The Pokémon summons acid rain when it's hit by an attack.
72 Oblivious 2 The Pokémon is oblivious, and that keeps it from being infatuated or taunted.

100 Simple 5 The stat changes the Pokémon receives are doubled.
